PrecisConfirmation of a "SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT" between the Crown, the Province of Ontario and THE GARDEN RIVER FIRST NATION AND BAND OF INDIANS whereby some 5,802 hectares of land situate in the Township of Kehoe, including mineral rights, will be set apart as an addition to Garden River Indian Reserve No. 14.
